All Classes

Class Description
BSController
The controller for the BSView.
BSModel
The all-important model for this game of battleship.
BSTest
JUnit test suite to show that the backend works great and to get all non-GUI and non-networking coverage.
BSView
This is the main-containing face of the battleship game.
Directions
A simple enum that tracks the orientation of the desired placed ship.
Move
Tracks if the type of move was a Hit or a Miss.
Ship
This object represents a Ship, which stores state such as its length, its name, whether or not it is sunk, its representation, and most importantly how many hits it has taken.
TestInitializer
I couldn't get JUnit's "Before" or "BeforeClass" methods to work, so this is a throwaway class for sets of points, comparisons, etc.
Turn
Server really just means "me" and client really just means "them" in regards to the mapping of Rectangle objects.
WhichGrid
A simple enum to see if the move concerns this grid, or the other grid.
